x^{\frac{2}{3}}-2x^{\frac{1}{3}}-3=0
\;x^{1/3} = t.\quad
t
t
x
\;\bf t = x^{1/3}.\;
\begin{align} x^{\large \frac{2}{3}}-2x^{\large \frac{1}{3}}-3= \left(x^{\large \frac{1}{3}}\right)^2 -2x^{\frac{1}{3}}-3=0 & \iff t^2 - 2t - 3 = 0 \\ \\ & \iff (t - 3)(t+1) = 0 \\ \\ & \iff t = 3 \;\text{ or } \;\; t = -1 \\ \\ & \iff {\bf t = x^{1/3}} = 3 \;\;\text{ or }\;\; {\bf t = x^{1/3}} = -1 \\ \\ &\iff x = (3)^3 \;\;\text{ or }\;\; x = (-1)^3 \\ \\ &\iff  x = 27 \;\;\text{ or }\;\; x = -1\end{align}
